Class AbstractMapLayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.maxstupo.flatengine.map.layer.AbstractMapLayer
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ObjectLayer, TileLayer

    public abstract class AbstractMapLayer
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is the base for all map layers (e.g. tile/object layers).
    Author:
    Maxstupo

      • doRender

        public void doRender(java.awt.Graphics2D g,
                     Camera camera)
        Calls render(Graphics2D, Camera) with the correct composite. If this layer is not visible or is transparent render(Graphics2D, Camera) won't be called.
        Parameters:
        g - the graphics context to render to.
        camera - the camera.
